    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level E92 M3, powered by the high-revving, naturally aspirated S65 4.0L V8. This specimen features a flawless carbon fiber roof and an interior with zero leather shrinkage or bolster wear. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator service. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers instantaneous gear changes, paired with an M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for peak chassis response. This is a turnkey, investment-grade example with a meticulous service history.",
