      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and show no signs of bolstering wear or creasing. Every electronic component and switch functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively performed by authorized technicians. It comes complete with both original keys, all owner manuals, and a set of untouched factory floor mats. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
