      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I have babied this car since the day I got it, and it's still in that perfect, 'just-off-the-lot' condition. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage, strictly hand-washed, and honestly, it looks and drives like a total dream! I\u2019m only selling because our family is growing, but I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will appreciate just how pristine this ride is. It\u2019s practically brand new and ready for a new home. Let's get you in for a test drive!",
