      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed, eliminating common chassis and internal vulnerabilities. Finished in a flawless factory coat with zero clear-coat failure, this car retains its original suspension geometry and bushing integrity, providing the tactile feedback and mechanical purity today's turbocharged models lack.",
